datamodel:
generator client {
  provider = "dart run orm"
  output   = "../lib/src/generated/prisma_client"
}

datasource db {
  provider = "mysql"
  url      = env("DATABASE_URL")
}

model user {
  id              Int       @id @default(autoincrement())
  uuid            String?   @unique(map: "User_uuid_key")
  name            String?
  lastname        String?
  email           String?   @unique(map: "User_email_key")
  phone           String?
  password        String?
  birthday        String?
  gender          String?
  role            user_role @default(USER)
  email_verify_at String?
  phone_verify_at String?
  img_profile     String?
  verify_token    String?
  verify_code     String?
  my_referral     String?
  referral        String?
  location        String?
  create_at       String?
  update_at       String?
}

model banner {
  id        Int     @id @default(autoincrement())
  url       String?
  type      String?
  img       String?
  active    String?
  create_at String?
  update_at String?
  delete_at String?
}

enum user_role {
  USER
  ADMIN
  VENDOR
  AGENTE
}
